{
  "id": "62ecbdd311b2150023a6af12",
  "title": "危機的な状況を表す四字熟語",
  "created": 1659682261,
  "updated": 1659683241,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "62ecbdd311b2150023a6af12",
      "text": "危機的な状況を表す四字熟語",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1659682261,
      "updated": 1659682261
    },
    {
      "id": "62ecbdd5e600350000efe784",
      "text": "一縷千鈞",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1659682261,
      "updated": 1659682262
    },
    {
      "id": "62ecbdd6e600350000efe785",
      "text": "　一髪千鈞",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1659682262,
      "updated": 1659682262
    },
    {
      "id": "62ecbdd6e600350000efe786",
      "text": "　千鈞一髪",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1659682262,
      "updated": 1659682262
    },
    {
      "id": "62ecbdd6e600350000efe787",
      "text": "一触即発",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1659682262,
      "updated": 1659682262
    },
    {
      "id": "62ecbdd6e600350000efe788",
      "text": "燕巣幕上",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1659682262,
      "updated": 1659682262
    },
    {
      "id": "62ecbdd6e600350000efe789",
      "text": "餓狼之口",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1659682262,
      "updated": 1659682262
    },
    {
      "id": "62ecbdd6e600350000efe78a",
      "text": "危急存亡",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1659682262,
      "updated": 1659682262
    },
    {
      "id": "62ecbdd6e600350000efe78b",
      "text": "虎尾春氷（こびしゅんぴょう）",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1659682262,
      "updated": 1659682262
    },
    {
      "id": "62ecbdd6e600350000efe78c",
      "text": "　>極めて危険なことのたとえ。または、危険なことをすることのたとえ。[虎]の尾を踏んで、春の厚みの無い氷の上を歩くという意味から。「虎尾春冰」とも書く。",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1659682262,
      "updated": 1659682262
    },
    {
      "id": "62ecbdd6e600350000efe78d",
      "text": "　出典：『[書経]』「君牙」",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1659682262,
      "updated": 1659682262
    },
    {
      "id": "62ecbdd6e600350000efe78e",
      "text": "小水之魚",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1659682262,
      "updated": 1659682262
    },
    {
      "id": "62ecbdd6e600350000efe78f",
      "text": "　涸轍鮒魚",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1659682262,
      "updated": 1659682262
    },
    {
      "id": "62ecbdd6e600350000efe790",
      "text": "　轍鮒之急",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1659682262,
      "updated": 1659682262
    },
    {
      "id": "62ecbdd6e600350000efe791",
      "text": "断崖絶壁",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1659682262,
      "updated": 1659682262
    },
    {
      "id": "62ecbdd6e600350000efe792",
      "text": "重卵之危",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1659682262,
      "updated": 1659682262
    },
    {
      "id": "62ecbdd6e600350000efe793",
      "text": "　累卵之危",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1659682262,
      "updated": 1659682262
    },
    {
      "id": "62ecbdd6e600350000efe794",
      "text": "白虹貫日",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1659682262,
      "updated": 1659682262
    },
    {
      "id": "62ecbdd6e600350000efe795",
      "text": "風前之灯",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1659682262,
      "updated": 1659682262
    },
    {
      "id": "62ecbdd6e600350000efe796",
      "text": "釜底游魚（ふていのゆうぎょ）",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1659682262,
      "updated": 1659682262
    },
    {
      "id": "62ecbdd6e600350000efe797",
      "text": "　>死が目の前に近づいていることのたとえ。火に掛けられ、煮られる寸前の釜の中を泳いでいる魚ということから。「釜底遊魚」とも書く。",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1659682262,
      "updated": 1659682262
    },
    {
      "id": "62ecbdd6e600350000efe798",
      "text": "　出典：『[後漢書]』「張綱伝」",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1659682262,
      "updated": 1659682262
    },
    {
      "id": "62ecbdd6e600350000efe799",
      "text": "奔車朽索（ほんしゃきゅうさく）",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1659682262,
      "updated": 1659682262
    },
    {
      "id": "62ecbdd6e600350000efe79a",
      "text": "　>非常に危険な状態のたとえ。「奔車」はどうなるか考えずに、速度を出した車。「朽索」は腐ってぼろぼろになった縄。どちらも危険な状態をいう言葉で、他人に注意を促すときにも使われる言葉。",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1659682262,
      "updated": 1659682262
    },
    {
      "id": "62ecbdd6e600350000efe79b",
      "text": "　出典：魏徴「諫太宗十思疏」",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1659682262,
      "updated": 1659682262
    },
    {
      "id": "62ecbdd6e600350000efe79c",
      "text": "[https://yoji.jitenon.jp/bamen/list103.html 「危険」場面・用途・意味が共通する四字熟語一覧]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1659682262,
      "updated": 1659682262
    },
    {
      "id": "62ecbdd6e600350000efe79d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1659682262,
      "updated": 1659682262
    },
    {
      "id": "62ecbdd6e600350000efe79e",
      "text": "[絶体絶命]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1659682262,
      "updated": 1659683241
    },
    {
      "id": "62ecbdd6e600350000efe79f",
      "text": "焦眉之急",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1659682262,
      "updated": 1659682262
    },
    {
      "id": "62ecbdd6e600350000efe7a0",
      "text": "　燃眉之急",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1659682262,
      "updated": 1659682262
    },
    {
      "id": "62ecbddce600350000efe7a1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1659682269,
      "updated": 1659682270
    },
    {
      "id": "62ecbddde600350000efe7a2",
      "text": "[四字熟語]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
